title: Basshunter - Calling Time (South African Version)
description: Hey guys! Bought this from South Africa to share with you guys! Please read the "readme" and PLEASE seed. Don't download and remove. This is a brand new torrent and the only one as of right now so support and love it like a child! Also please say thanks for my purchase and sharing. I know your not going to be happy I didn't rip it through iTunes or something like that but the first sharing should be as authentic to the original as possible. Just burn the .cue file to a blank CD using a good ISO burning software and then you can rip it and tag it yourself how you like. I would also like to say after you enjoy this version, you should buy the American/UK version when it releases July 23rd, 2013 to support the artist. I think this album will make you WANT to buy the real thing.
